visual.name: GanttChartByMAQSoftware
visual.description: A Gantt Chart with added grid, having the capability to provide additional details of task or schedule along with KPIs

columnOutline.description: Select the location for the outline in column header

fontFamily.description: Select the font-family for column headers
Select the font-family for category labels

position.description: Select the location for the label

fontFamily.description: Select the font-family for data labels

displayRatio.description: Aspect ratio of category labels and gantt chart
